oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Lake view Dunbar Cave, Idaho Springs Hotel, Clarksville, Tenn.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Color tinted and enhanced photograph of two unidentified people looking over a fence at a lake near Dunbar Cave. Features a divided back and narrative on reverse. There is a (partially obscured) logo for E.C. Kropp Co. around the stamp box in the upper right corner. Postcard printed on linen and made in the United States of America. Note: there is surface damage on the back side of this postcard. [No. 23752 N]
